### inserts a new customer

POST {{host}}/insert
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
    "name": "Stefania",
    "age": 32,
    "favouriteDestinations": {
        "destinations": [
            {
                "city": "Rochester"
            }
        ]
    }
}

### find by name

GET {{host}}/find?name=Stefania
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

### find by id

GET {{host}}/findById?id=1
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

